io.artframework

Interface FinderResult<TResult>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TResult>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFinderResult, ArtObjectFinder.ArtObjectFinderResult, ModuleFinder.ModuleFinderResult, TargetFinder.TargetFinderResult

    public interface FinderResult<TResult>
extends java.lang.Iterable<TResult>
    Contains all result objects and errors that were found during a find operation with a finder.

    Each finder result should have a corresponding AbstractFinder implementation that produces the result.

    Implementation notice

    The underlying result must be immutable and should only be directly produced by the corresponding finder.
